author: RTÉ News
title: China's new Covid-19 cases rises to six-week high
description: China's north-eastern border with Russia has become a front line in the fight against a resurgence of the Covid-19 pandemic as new daily cases rose to the highest in nearly six weeks - with more than 90% involving people coming from abroad.
